                <h1>Discover the Iconic BMW Logo: Meaning & History</h1>
                <p>The BMW logo, a symbol of luxury and engineering excellence, consists of a circular design divided into four quadrants of blue and white. This striking emblem reflects the company's roots in aviation, with its colors inspired by the Bavarian flag. Since its inception, it has become synonymous with performance and prestige in the automotive industry.</p>
